    "# NLP Sentiment Analysis"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "bb13e9be",

    "id": "bb13e9be"
   },
   "source": [
    "### Business Objective:"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "f7ad4ff8",
   "metadata": {
    "id": "f7ad4ff8"
   },
   "source": [
    "- Extracting sentiment from customer reviews on a product\n",
    "- Data Set Details:\n",
    "\n",
    "The dataset should be scraped/extracted form ecommerce websites like amazon etc. \n",
    "\n",
    "Preferably amazon and focus only on extracting customer reviews, rest are not required\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "f0eff57f",
   "metadata": {
    "id": "f0eff57f"
   },
   "source": [
    "## Data Collection"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "db518f9c",
   "metadata": {
    "id": "db518f9c"
   },
   "source": [
    "* Product : Apple 2020 MacBook Air Laptop M1 chip, 13.3-inch\n",
    "* E-commerse website : www.amazon.in"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "42aff3ac",
   "metadata": {
    "id": "42aff3ac"
   },
   "source": [
    "MacBook Air was the first product in Mac series launched with the M1 chip produced by Apple itself, which replaced the Intel Prossesors in Apple products. \n",
    "Apple integrated the CPU, GPU, Neural Engine, I/O and so much more onto a single tiny chip. M1 delivers exceptional performance, custom technologies and unbelievable power efficiency. Introduction of M1 chip was considered as a major breakthrough for Mac.\n",
    "\n",
    "This gives a relevence in analyzing the customer reviews about the new product from a e-commerse website.\n",
    "\n",
    "Link : https://www.amazon.in/Apple-MacBook-Chip-13-inch-256GB/product-reviews/B08N5W4NNB/ref=cm_cr_dp_d_show_all_btm?ie=UTF8&reviewerType=all_reviews"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "ac0e6d47",
   "metadata": {
    "id": "ac0e6d47"
   },
   "source": [

    "# Removing emojis from reviews\n",
    "import re\n",
    "\n",
    "# Define the emoji pattern\n",
    "emoji_pattern = re.compile(\"[\"\n",
    "        u\"\\U0001F600-\\U0001F64F\"  # emoticons\n",
    "        u\"\\U0001F300-\\U0001F5FF\"  # symbols & pictographs\n",
    "        u\"\\U0001F680-\\U0001F6FF\"  # transport & map symbols\n",
    "        u\"\\U0001F1E0-\\U0001F1FF\"  \n",
    "        u\"\\U00002702-\\U000027B0\"\n",
    "        u\"\\U000024C2-\\U0001F251\"\n",
    "        u\"\\U0001F9D0-\\U0001F9DF\"\n",
    "                           \"]+\", flags=re.UNICODE)"
   ]

    "# Creating sentiment column\n",
    "\n",
    "def get_sentiment_label(text):\n",
    "    sentiment = TextBlob(text).sentiment.polarity\n",
    "    if sentiment > 0:\n",
    "        return 'Positive'\n",
    "    elif sentiment < 0:\n",
    "        return 'Negative'\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        return 'Neutral'"
   ]
  },

    "neutral=review[review['Sentiment']=='Neutral']\n",
    "neutral\n",
    "\n",
    "# Joining the list into one string/text\n",
    "neutral_j=''.join(neutral['Content'])\n",
    "\n",
    "# Removing Punctuation\n",
    "neutral_nop=neutral_j.translate(str.maketrans('','',string.punctuation))\n",
    "\n",
    "# Tokanization\n",
    "neutral_token=word_tokenize(neutral_nop)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Removing stopwords\n",
    "neutral_nosw=[word for word in neutral_token if not word in stop]\n",
    "\n",
    "df_neu=pd.DataFrame({'rev':neutral_nosw})\n",
    "df_neu\n",
    "\n",
    "# concatenate the preprocessed text into a single string\n",
    "neutral_w=' '.join(df_neu['rev'])\n",
    "\n",
    "# create the word cloud\n",
    "wordcloud_neu = WordCloud(width=800, height=800, background_color='black', min_font_size=10).generate(neutral_w)\n",
    "\n",
    "# plot the word cloud\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(8, 8), facecolor=None)\n",
    "plt.imshow(wordcloud_neu)\n",
    "plt.axis('off')\n",
    "plt.tight_layout(pad=0)\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
